Oply 2.2 — Changelog

Added Oply Radio: new standalone radio player GUI.

Added Oply IPTV/TV integration inside Oply Video.

Oply Video: country/locale indexing for IPTV lists (per-user config under ~/.config/oply/, no root usage).

Oply Video: IPTV channel selector moved to a separate window so playback uses the full player area.

Oply Video: added “Connecting…” overlay while a stream starts (better feedback during black screen/buffering).

Oply Radio: added minimize to tray with tray menu and localized labels.

Oply Radio: added favorites (right-click add/remove), favorites list accessible from the heart button, and “★ Favorites” in the country selector.

Oply Radio: improved shutdown so the app fully exits (no background process left running).

Oply (Audio): restored Radio launcher button and added Video launcher button in the headerbar; icons scaled to match existing UI.

Added .desktop launcher for Oply Radio with the correct icon and executable path.

Updated About dialog to mention the new Radio and IPTV integrations (translated in supported languages).


